{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"We've got a real problem with math education right now."},{"time":4000,"text":"Basically, no one's very happy."},{"time":7000,"text":"Those learning it"},{"time":9000,"text":"think it's disconnected,"},{"time":11000,"text":"uninteresting and hard."},{"time":13000,"text":"Those trying to employ them"},{"time":15000,"text":"think they don't know enough."},{"time":17000,"text":"Governments realize that it's a big deal for our economies,"},{"time":20000,"text":"but don't know how to fix it."},{"time":23000,"text":"And teachers are also frustrated."},{"time":25000,"text":"Yet math is more important to the world"},{"time":28000,"text":"than at any point in human history."},{"time":30000,"text":"So at one end we've got falling interest"},{"time":32000,"text":"in education in math,"},{"time":34000,"text":"and at the other end we've got a more mathematical world,"},{"time":37000,"text":"a more quantitative world than we ever have had."}]},{"cues":[{"time":41000,"text":"So what's the problem, why has this chasm opened up,"},{"time":43000,"text":"and what can we do to fix it?"},{"time":46000,"text":"Well actually, I think the answer"},{"time":48000,"text":"is staring us right in the face:"},{"time":50000,"text":"Use computers."},{"time":52000,"text":"I believe"},{"time":54000,"text":"that correctly using computers"},{"time":56000,"text":"is the silver bullet"},{"time":58000,"text":"for making math education work."},{"time":61000,"text":"So to explain that,"},{"time":63000,"text":"let me first talk a bit about what math looks like in the real world"},{"time":66000,"text":"and what it looks like in education."},{"time":68000,"text":"See, in the real world"},{"time":70000,"text":"math isn't necessarily done by mathematicians."},{"time":73000,"text":"It's done by geologists,"},{"time":75000,"text":"engineers, biologists,"},{"time":77000,"text":"all sorts of different people --"},{"time":79000,"text":"modeling and simulation."},{"time":81000,"text":"It's actually very popular."},{"time":83000,"text":"But in education it looks very different --"},{"time":86000,"text":"dumbed-down problems, lots of calculating,"},{"time":88000,"text":"mostly by hand."},{"time":91000,"text":"Lots of things that seem simple"},{"time":93000,"text":"and not difficult like in the real world,"},{"time":95000,"text":"except if you're learning it."},{"time":98000,"text":"And another thing about math:"},{"time":100000,"text":"math sometimes looks like math --"},{"time":102000,"text":"like in this example here --"},{"time":105000,"text":"and sometimes it doesn't --"},{"time":107000,"text":"like \"Am I drunk?\""},{"time":112000,"text":"And then you get an answer that's quantitative in the modern world."},{"time":115000,"text":"You wouldn't have expected that a few years back."},{"time":118000,"text":"But now you can find out all about --"},{"time":121000,"text":"unfortunately, my weight is a little higher than that, but --"},{"time":124000,"text":"all about what happens."}]},{"cues":[{"time":126000,"text":"So let's zoom out a bit and ask,"},{"time":128000,"text":"why are we teaching people math?"},{"time":130000,"text":"What's the point of teaching people math?"},{"time":133000,"text":"And in particular, why are we teaching them math in general?"},{"time":136000,"text":"Why is it such an important part of education"},{"time":139000,"text":"as a sort of compulsory subject?"},{"time":141000,"text":"Well, I think there are about three reasons:"},{"time":144000,"text":"technical jobs"},{"time":146000,"text":"so critical to the development of our economies,"},{"time":149000,"text":"what I call \"everyday living\" --"},{"time":153000,"text":"to function in the world today,"},{"time":155000,"text":"you've got to be pretty quantitative,"},{"time":157000,"text":"much more so than a few years ago:"},{"time":159000,"text":"figure out your mortgages,"},{"time":161000,"text":"being skeptical of government statistics, those kinds of things --"},{"time":165000,"text":"and thirdly, what I would call something like"},{"time":168000,"text":"logical mind training, logical thinking."},{"time":171000,"text":"Over the years"},{"time":173000,"text":"we've put so much in society"},{"time":175000,"text":"into being able to process and think logically. It's part of human society."},{"time":178000,"text":"It's very important to learn that"},{"time":180000,"text":"math is a great way to do that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":182000,"text":"So let's ask another question."},{"time":184000,"text":"What is math?"},{"time":186000,"text":"What do we mean when we say we're doing math,"},{"time":188000,"text":"or educating people to do math?"},{"time":190000,"text":"Well, I think it's about four steps, roughly speaking,"},{"time":193000,"text":"starting with posing the right question."},{"time":195000,"text":"What is it that we want to ask? What is it we're trying to find out here?"},{"time":198000,"text":"And this is the thing most screwed up in the outside world,"},{"time":200000,"text":"beyond virtually any other part of doing math."},{"time":203000,"text":"People ask the wrong question,"},{"time":205000,"text":"and surprisingly enough, they get the wrong answer,"},{"time":207000,"text":"for that reason, if not for others."},{"time":209000,"text":"So the next thing is take that problem"},{"time":211000,"text":"and turn it from a real world problem"},{"time":213000,"text":"into a math problem."},{"time":215000,"text":"That's stage two."},{"time":217000,"text":"Once you've done that, then there's the computation step."},{"time":220000,"text":"Turn it from that into some answer"},{"time":222000,"text":"in a mathematical form."},{"time":225000,"text":"And of course, math is very powerful at doing that."},{"time":227000,"text":"And then finally, turn it back to the real world."},{"time":229000,"text":"Did it answer the question?"},{"time":231000,"text":"And also verify it -- crucial step."},{"time":235000,"text":"Now here's the crazy thing right now."},{"time":237000,"text":"In math education,"},{"time":239000,"text":"we're spending about perhaps 80 percent of the time"},{"time":242000,"text":"teaching people to do step three by hand."},{"time":245000,"text":"Yet, that's the one step computers can do"},{"time":247000,"text":"better than any human after years of practice."},{"time":250000,"text":"Instead, we ought to be using computers"},{"time":253000,"text":"to do step three"},{"time":255000,"text":"and using the students to spend much more effort"},{"time":258000,"text":"on learning how to do steps one, two and four --"},{"time":260000,"text":"conceptualizing problems, applying them,"},{"time":263000,"text":"getting the teacher to run them through how to do that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":266000,"text":"See, crucial point here:"},{"time":268000,"text":"math is not equal to calculating."},{"time":270000,"text":"Math is a much broader subject than calculating."},{"time":273000,"text":"Now it's understandable that this has all got intertwined"},{"time":276000,"text":"over hundreds of years."},{"time":278000,"text":"There was only one way to do calculating and that was by hand."},{"time":281000,"text":"But in the last few decades"},{"time":283000,"text":"that has totally changed."},{"time":285000,"text":"We've had the biggest transformation of any ancient subject"},{"time":288000,"text":"that I could ever imagine with computers."},{"time":292000,"text":"Calculating was typically the limiting step,"},{"time":294000,"text":"and now often it isn't."},{"time":296000,"text":"So I think in terms of the fact that math"},{"time":298000,"text":"has been liberated from calculating."},{"time":301000,"text":"But that math liberation didn't get into education yet."},{"time":304000,"text":"See, I think of calculating, in a sense,"},{"time":306000,"text":"as the machinery of math."},{"time":308000,"text":"It's the chore."},{"time":310000,"text":"It's the thing you'd like to avoid if you can, like to get a machine to do."},{"time":314000,"text":"It's a means to an end, not an end in itself,"},{"time":319000,"text":"and automation allows us"},{"time":321000,"text":"to have that machinery."},{"time":323000,"text":"Computers allow us to do that --"},{"time":325000,"text":"and this is not a small problem by any means."},{"time":328000,"text":"I estimated that, just today, across the world,"},{"time":331000,"text":"we spent about 106 average world lifetimes"},{"time":334000,"text":"teaching people how to calculate by hand."},{"time":337000,"text":"That's an amazing amount of human endeavor."},{"time":340000,"text":"So we better be damn sure --"},{"time":342000,"text":"and by the way, they didn't even have fun doing it, most of them --"},{"time":345000,"text":"so we better be damn sure"},{"time":347000,"text":"that we know why we're doing that"},{"time":349000,"text":"and it has a real purpose."}]},{"cues":[{"time":351000,"text":"I think we should be assuming computers"},{"time":353000,"text":"for doing the calculating"},{"time":355000,"text":"and only doing hand calculations where it really makes sense to teach people that."},{"time":358000,"text":"And I think there are some cases."},{"time":360000,"text":"For example: mental arithmetic."},{"time":362000,"text":"I still do a lot of that, mainly for estimating."},{"time":365000,"text":"People say, \"Is such and such true?\""},{"time":367000,"text":"And I'll say, \"Hmm, not sure.\" I'll think about it roughly."},{"time":369000,"text":"It's still quicker to do that and more practical."},{"time":371000,"text":"So I think practicality is one case"},{"time":373000,"text":"where it's worth teaching people by hand."},{"time":375000,"text":"And then there are certain conceptual things"},{"time":377000,"text":"that can also benefit from hand calculating,"},{"time":379000,"text":"but I think they're relatively small in number."},{"time":381000,"text":"One thing I often ask about"},{"time":383000,"text":"is ancient Greek and how this relates."},{"time":386000,"text":"See, the thing we're doing right now"},{"time":388000,"text":"is we're forcing people to learn mathematics."},{"time":390000,"text":"It's a major subject."},{"time":392000,"text":"I'm not for one minute suggesting that, if people are interested in hand calculating"},{"time":395000,"text":"or in following their own interests"},{"time":397000,"text":"in any subject however bizarre --"},{"time":399000,"text":"they should do that."},{"time":401000,"text":"That's absolutely the right thing,"},{"time":403000,"text":"for people to follow their self-interest."},{"time":405000,"text":"I was somewhat interested in ancient Greek,"},{"time":407000,"text":"but I don't think that we should force the entire population"},{"time":410000,"text":"to learn a subject like ancient Greek."},{"time":412000,"text":"I don't think it's warranted."},{"time":414000,"text":"So I have this distinction between what we're making people do"},{"time":417000,"text":"and the subject that's sort of mainstream"},{"time":419000,"text":"and the subject that, in a sense, people might follow with their own interest"},{"time":422000,"text":"and perhaps even be spiked into doing that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":424000,"text":"So what are the issues people bring up with this?"},{"time":427000,"text":"Well one of them is, they say, you need to get the basics first."},{"time":430000,"text":"You shouldn't use the machine"},{"time":432000,"text":"until you get the basics of the subject."},{"time":434000,"text":"So my usual question is, what do you mean by \"basics?\""},{"time":437000,"text":"Basics of what?"},{"time":439000,"text":"Are the basics of driving a car"},{"time":441000,"text":"learning how to service it, or design it for that matter?"},{"time":444000,"text":"Are the basics of writing learning how to sharpen a quill?"},{"time":448000,"text":"I don't think so."},{"time":450000,"text":"I think you need to separate the basics of what you're trying to do"},{"time":453000,"text":"from how it gets done"},{"time":455000,"text":"and the machinery of how it gets done"},{"time":459000,"text":"and automation allows you to make that separation."},{"time":462000,"text":"A hundred years ago, it's certainly true that to drive a car"},{"time":465000,"text":"you kind of needed to know a lot about the mechanics of the car"},{"time":467000,"text":"and how the ignition timing worked and all sorts of things."},{"time":471000,"text":"But automation in cars"},{"time":473000,"text":"allowed that to separate,"},{"time":475000,"text":"so driving is now a quite separate subject, so to speak,"},{"time":478000,"text":"from engineering of the car"},{"time":481000,"text":"or learning how to service it."},{"time":485000,"text":"So automation allows this separation"},{"time":487000,"text":"and also allows -- in the case of driving,"},{"time":489000,"text":"and I believe also in the future case of maths --"},{"time":491000,"text":"a democratized way of doing that."},{"time":493000,"text":"It can be spread across a much larger number of people"},{"time":495000,"text":"who can really work with that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":498000,"text":"So there's another thing that comes up with basics."},{"time":500000,"text":"People confuse, in my view,"},{"time":502000,"text":"the order of the invention of the tools"},{"time":505000,"text":"with the order in which they should use them for teaching."},{"time":508000,"text":"So just because paper was invented before computers,"},{"time":511000,"text":"it doesn't necessarily mean you get more to the basics of the subject"},{"time":514000,"text":"by using paper instead of a computer"},{"time":516000,"text":"to teach mathematics."},{"time":520000,"text":"My daughter gave me a rather nice anecdote on this."},{"time":523000,"text":"She enjoys making what she calls \"paper laptops.\""},{"time":526000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":528000,"text":"So I asked her one day, \"You know, when I was your age,"},{"time":530000,"text":"I didn't make these."},{"time":532000,"text":"Why do you think that was?\""},{"time":534000,"text":"And after a second or two, carefully reflecting,"},{"time":536000,"text":"she said, \"No paper?\""},{"time":538000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":544000,"text":"If you were born after computers and paper,"},{"time":546000,"text":"it doesn't really matter which order you're taught with them in,"},{"time":549000,"text":"you just want to have the best tool."}]},{"cues":[{"time":551000,"text":"So another one that comes up is \"Computers dumb math down.\""},{"time":554000,"text":"That somehow, if you use a computer,"},{"time":556000,"text":"it's all mindless button-pushing,"},{"time":558000,"text":"but if you do it by hand,"},{"time":560000,"text":"it's all intellectual."},{"time":562000,"text":"This one kind of annoys me, I must say."},{"time":565000,"text":"Do we really believe"},{"time":567000,"text":"that the math that most people are doing in school"},{"time":569000,"text":"practically today"},{"time":571000,"text":"is more than applying procedures"},{"time":573000,"text":"to problems they don't really understand, for reasons they don't get?"},{"time":576000,"text":"I don't think so."},{"time":578000,"text":"And what's worse, what they're learning there isn't even practically useful anymore."},{"time":581000,"text":"Might have been 50 years ago, but it isn't anymore."},{"time":584000,"text":"When they're out of education, they do it on a computer."},{"time":587000,"text":"Just to be clear, I think computers can really help with this problem,"},{"time":590000,"text":"actually make it more conceptual."},{"time":592000,"text":"Now, of course, like any great tool,"},{"time":594000,"text":"they can be used completely mindlessly,"},{"time":596000,"text":"like turning everything into a multimedia show,"},{"time":599000,"text":"like the example I was shown of solving an equation by hand,"},{"time":602000,"text":"where the computer was the teacher --"},{"time":604000,"text":"show the student how to manipulate and solve it by hand."},{"time":607000,"text":"This is just nuts."},{"time":609000,"text":"Why are we using computers to show a student how to solve a problem by hand"},{"time":612000,"text":"that the computer should be doing anyway?"},{"time":614000,"text":"All backwards."}]},{"cues":[{"time":616000,"text":"Let me show you"},{"time":618000,"text":"that you can also make problems harder to calculate."},{"time":621000,"text":"See, normally in school,"},{"time":623000,"text":"you do things like solve quadratic equations."},{"time":626000,"text":"But you see, when you're using a computer,"},{"time":629000,"text":"you can just substitute."},{"time":633000,"text":"You can make it a quartic equation. Make it kind of harder, calculating-wise."},{"time":635000,"text":"Same principles applied --"},{"time":637000,"text":"calculations, harder."},{"time":639000,"text":"And problems in the real world"},{"time":641000,"text":"look nutty and horrible like this."},{"time":643000,"text":"They've got hair all over them."},{"time":645000,"text":"They're not just simple, dumbed-down things that we see in school math."},{"time":649000,"text":"And think of the outside world."},{"time":651000,"text":"Do we really believe that engineering and biology"},{"time":653000,"text":"and all of these other things"},{"time":655000,"text":"that have so benefited from computers and maths"},{"time":657000,"text":"have somehow conceptually gotten reduced by using computers?"},{"time":660000,"text":"I don't think so -- quite the opposite."},{"time":663000,"text":"So the problem we've really got in math education"},{"time":666000,"text":"is not that computers might dumb it down,"},{"time":669000,"text":"but that we have dumbed-down problems right now."},{"time":672000,"text":"Well, another issue people bring up"},{"time":674000,"text":"is somehow that hand calculating procedures"},{"time":676000,"text":"teach understanding."},{"time":678000,"text":"So if you go through lots of examples,"},{"time":680000,"text":"you can get the answer,"},{"time":682000,"text":"you can understand how the basics of the system work better."},{"time":685000,"text":"I think there is one thing that I think very valid here,"},{"time":688000,"text":"which is that I think understanding procedures and processes is important."},{"time":692000,"text":"But there's a fantastic way to do that in the modern world."},{"time":695000,"text":"It's called programming."}]},{"cues":[{"time":698000,"text":"Programming is how most procedures and processes"},{"time":700000,"text":"get written down these days,"},{"time":702000,"text":"and it's also a great way"},{"time":704000,"text":"to engage students much more"},{"time":706000,"text":"and to check they really understand."},{"time":708000,"text":"If you really want to check you understand math"},{"time":710000,"text":"then write a program to do it."},{"time":713000,"text":"So programming is the way I think we should be doing that."},{"time":716000,"text":"So to be clear, what I really am suggesting here"},{"time":718000,"text":"is we have a unique opportunity"},{"time":720000,"text":"to make maths both more practical"},{"time":722000,"text":"and more conceptual, simultaneously."},{"time":725000,"text":"I can't think of any other subject where that's recently been possible."},{"time":728000,"text":"It's usually some kind of choice"},{"time":730000,"text":"between the vocational and the intellectual."},{"time":732000,"text":"But I think we can do both at the same time here."},{"time":737000,"text":"And we open up so many more possibilities."},{"time":740000,"text":"You can do so many more problems."},{"time":742000,"text":"What I really think we gain from this"},{"time":744000,"text":"is students getting intuition and experience"},{"time":747000,"text":"in far greater quantities than they've ever got before."},{"time":750000,"text":"And experience of harder problems --"},{"time":752000,"text":"being able to play with the math, interact with it,"},{"time":754000,"text":"feel it."},{"time":756000,"text":"We want people who can feel the math instinctively."},{"time":759000,"text":"That's what computers allow us to do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":762000,"text":"Another thing it allows us to do is reorder the curriculum."},{"time":765000,"text":"Traditionally it's been by how difficult it is to calculate,"},{"time":767000,"text":"but now we can reorder it"},{"time":769000,"text":"by how difficult it is to understand the concepts,"},{"time":771000,"text":"however hard the calculating."},{"time":773000,"text":"So calculus has traditionally been taught very late."},{"time":776000,"text":"Why is this?"},{"time":778000,"text":"Well, it's damn hard doing the calculations, that's the problem."},{"time":782000,"text":"But actually many of the concepts"},{"time":784000,"text":"are amenable to a much younger age group."},{"time":787000,"text":"This was an example I built for my daughter."},{"time":790000,"text":"And very, very simple."},{"time":793000,"text":"We were talking about what happens"},{"time":795000,"text":"when you increase the number of sides of a polygon"},{"time":797000,"text":"to a very large number."},{"time":801000,"text":"And of course, it turns into a circle."},{"time":803000,"text":"And by the way, she was also very insistent"},{"time":805000,"text":"on being able to change the color,"},{"time":807000,"text":"an important feature for this demonstration."},{"time":811000,"text":"You can see that this is a very early step"},{"time":814000,"text":"into limits and differential calculus"},{"time":816000,"text":"and what happens when you take things to an extreme --"},{"time":819000,"text":"and very small sides and a very large number of sides."},{"time":821000,"text":"Very simple example."},{"time":823000,"text":"That's a view of the world"},{"time":825000,"text":"that we don't usually give people for many, many years after this."},{"time":828000,"text":"And yet, that's a really important practical view of the world."},{"time":831000,"text":"So one of the roadblocks we have"},{"time":834000,"text":"in moving this agenda forward"},{"time":837000,"text":"is exams."},{"time":839000,"text":"In the end, if we test everyone by hand in exams,"},{"time":842000,"text":"it's kind of hard to get the curricula changed"},{"time":845000,"text":"to a point where they can use computers"},{"time":847000,"text":"during the semesters."}]},{"cues":[{"time":850000,"text":"And one of the reasons it's so important --"},{"time":852000,"text":"so it's very important to get computers in exams."},{"time":855000,"text":"And then we can ask questions, real questions,"},{"time":858000,"text":"questions like, what's the best life insurance policy to get? --"},{"time":861000,"text":"real questions that people have in their everyday lives."},{"time":865000,"text":"And you see, this isn't some dumbed-down model here."},{"time":867000,"text":"This is an actual model where we can be asked to optimize what happens."},{"time":870000,"text":"How many years of protection do I need?"},{"time":872000,"text":"What does that do to the payments"},{"time":874000,"text":"and to the interest rates and so forth?"},{"time":877000,"text":"Now I'm not for one minute suggesting it's the only kind of question"},{"time":880000,"text":"that should be asked in exams,"},{"time":882000,"text":"but I think it's a very important type"},{"time":884000,"text":"that right now just gets completely ignored"},{"time":887000,"text":"and is critical for people's real understanding."}]},{"cues":[{"time":890000,"text":"So I believe [there is] critical reform"},{"time":893000,"text":"we have to do in computer-based math."},{"time":895000,"text":"We have got to make sure"},{"time":897000,"text":"that we can move our economies forward,"},{"time":900000,"text":"and also our societies,"},{"time":902000,"text":"based on the idea that people can really feel mathematics."},{"time":907000,"text":"This isn't some optional extra."},{"time":910000,"text":"And the country that does this first"},{"time":912000,"text":"will, in my view, leapfrog others"},{"time":915000,"text":"in achieving a new economy even,"},{"time":918000,"text":"an improved economy,"},{"time":920000,"text":"an improved outlook."},{"time":922000,"text":"In fact, I even talk about us moving"},{"time":924000,"text":"from what we often call now the \"knowledge economy\""},{"time":927000,"text":"to what we might call a \"computational knowledge economy,\""},{"time":930000,"text":"where high-level math is integral to what everyone does"},{"time":933000,"text":"in the way that knowledge currently is."},{"time":935000,"text":"We can engage so many more students with this,"},{"time":938000,"text":"and they can have a better time doing it."},{"time":941000,"text":"And let's understand:"},{"time":943000,"text":"this is not an incremental sort of change."},{"time":947000,"text":"We're trying to cross the chasm here"},{"time":949000,"text":"between school math and the real-world math."},{"time":951000,"text":"And you know if you walk across a chasm,"},{"time":953000,"text":"you end up making it worse than if you didn't start at all --"},{"time":956000,"text":"bigger disaster."},{"time":958000,"text":"No, what I'm suggesting"},{"time":960000,"text":"is that we should leap off,"},{"time":962000,"text":"we should increase our velocity"},{"time":964000,"text":"so it's high,"},{"time":966000,"text":"and we should leap off one side and go the other --"},{"time":969000,"text":"of course, having calculated our differential equation very carefully."}]},{"cues":[{"time":972000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":974000,"text":"So I want to see"},{"time":976000,"text":"a completely renewed, changed math curriculum"},{"time":978000,"text":"built from the ground up,"},{"time":980000,"text":"based on computers being there,"},{"time":982000,"text":"computers that are now ubiquitous almost."},{"time":984000,"text":"Calculating machines are everywhere"},{"time":986000,"text":"and will be completely everywhere in a small number of years."},{"time":989000,"text":"Now I'm not even sure if we should brand the subject as math,"},{"time":993000,"text":"but what I am sure is"},{"time":995000,"text":"it's the mainstream subject of the future."},{"time":998000,"text":"Let's go for it,"},{"time":1001000,"text":"and while we're about it,"},{"time":1003000,"text":"let's have a bit of fun,"},{"time":1005000,"text":"for us, for the students and for TED here."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1008000,"text":"Thanks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1010000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}